'From Squeakland 3.8.5976 of 25 August 2004 [latest update: #402] on 15 March 2005 at 7:40:23 pm'!"Change Set:		setDropShadow-sw=Date:			15 March 2005Author:			Scott WallaceFix up the setter of dropShadow so that you can correctly set the drop shadow of a rotated morph from a viewer."!!Player methodsFor: 'slot getters/setters' stamp: 'sw 3/15/2005 18:23'!setDropShadow: aValue	"Setter for costume's dropShadow"	| aMorph |	(aMorph _ costume renderedMorph) hasDropShadow ~~ aValue ifTrue: [aMorph toggleDropShadow]! !